# Badge — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/badge.css`

## Architecture

ALL styling in CSS via `@apply` + raw CSS. React only composes class names via `clsx`.

## CSS Classes

### Base
`.acko-badge` — `inline-flex items-center gap-1 font-medium whitespace-nowrap rounded-full leading-none`

### Sizes
| Class | Padding | Font |
|-------|---------|------|
| `.acko-badge-sm` | `--space-1` (4px) | `--font-label-sm-size` |
| `.acko-badge-md` | `--scale-6` (6px) | `--font-caption-size` |
| `.acko-badge-lg` | `--space-2` (8px) | `--font-body-sm-size` |

### Solid Variant Colors
Pattern: `.acko-badge-solid-{color}` where color = `purple | green | blue | orange | pink | gray`

Uses tokens: `--color-badge-{color}-bg`, `--color-badge-{color}-text`, `--color-badge-{color}-shadow-top`

### Outline Variant Colors
Pattern: `.acko-badge-outline-{color}`

Uses token: `--color-badge-{color}-outline-color` for both text and border

### Dot Variant Colors
Pattern: `.acko-badge-dot-{color}`

Same bg as solid + `.acko-badge-dot` child element (`--scale-6` circle in `currentColor`)

### Children
- `.acko-badge-dot` — `--scale-6` circle indicator
- `.acko-badge-remove` — remove button with X icon (`--scale-12` SVG)

### Counter Badge
- `.acko-counter-badge` — pill with min-width `--scale-20`, height `--scale-20`, padding `0 --scale-6`, font `--font-label-sm-size`, tabular-nums
- `.acko-counter-badge-{color}` — purple, pink, blue
